Package com.brestats.model.data

Class Aeroport

java.lang.Object
com.brestats.model.data.Aeroport
All Implemented Interfaces:
Model
public class Aeroport extends Object implements Model
The Aeroport class represents an airport with specific attributes such as its name, address, and associated department. It implements the Model interface and provides methods to access and manipulate its data.

This class includes methods to get and set the airport's name, address, and department, as well as to return a string representation of the airport.
